description: The Tamale Company is all about quality - you can tell when you unwrap one of their golden corn husks and out rolls a beautifully-steamed tamale, delicate and light yet rich with the flavors of authentic Mexican spices, velvety cheeses, and deliciously seasoned meats. Gluten and lard-free, these premium tamales have become quite a hot commodity at the farmer’s markets around Dallas. Thankfully, The Tamale Company has the heart to cart out to you too. With several catering options including push carts, chips + salsa bars, etc… you’ll be in good company with these fine Texas tamales!
name: The Tamale Company
